<taxonomicName authorityName="Temminck" authorityYear="1835" box="[2095,2283,1569,1609]" class="Mammalia" family="Rhinolophidae" genus="Rhinolophus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="318" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="euryotis">
<emphasis box="[2095,2283,1569,1609]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="318">R. euryotis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs between Sulawesi and New 
<collectingCountry box="[2970,3109,1569,1608]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="39" pageNumber="318">Guinea</collectingCountry>
have not been tested phylogenetically or morphometrically, and some or all of these populations could potentially refer to 
